@73803  = ~SHADOW DRUID: Shadow druids are a militant sect of druids who believe that there is a long and endless struggle between civilization and nature and that their role is to even the odds for nature.  They have been known to use extreme methods and violence to drive away civilization, using the ferocious powers of nature they are capable of summoning.

